{"id":8165,"date":"2026-01-22T17:00:18","date_gmt":"2026-01-22T10:00:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8165"},"modified":"2026-02-03T15:33:11","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T08:33:11","slug":"tinosorb-s-mang-loc-chong-nang-pho-rong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/tinosorb-s-mang-loc-chong-nang-pho-rong\/","title":{"rendered":"Tinosorb S \u2013 M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tinosorb S (BEMT) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u201cng\u00f4i sao\u201d c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, r\u1ea5t b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n<\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 avobenzone, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u0103ng c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gioi-thieu-chung-ve-tinosorb-s\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u chung v\u1ec1 Tinosorb S<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8167\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8167\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8167 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-2.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc tinosorb S\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8167\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc tinosorb S<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc\/INCI:<\/b> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol Methoxyphenyl Triazine<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (BEMT); t\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i Tinosorb S. Thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m triazine h\u1eefu c\u01a1, tan trong d\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c &amp; l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> BEMT \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 an to\u00e0n b\u1edfi \u1ee6y ban Khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a EU (SCCNFP\/SCCS) v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 10% trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00fd theo th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>EU v\u00e0 \u0111a s\u1ed1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ngo\u00e0i Hoa K\u1ef3:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn 10% trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8166\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8166\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8166 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-1.webp\" alt=\"Tinosorb S \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng kcn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8166\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tinosorb S \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng kcn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Hoa K\u1ef3:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i (10\/2025) ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t GRASE (an to\u00e0n &amp; hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn chung) trong OTC sunscreen; quy tr\u00ecnh OMOR \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn n\u0103m 2026.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-mang-loc-chong-nang-tinosorb-s\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng Tinosorb S<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng UVA\/UVB v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ea1nh cho UVA-PF v\u00e0 SPF, gi\u00fap m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng \u201cm\u00e1i che\u201d b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u1edf c\u1ea3 UVA1\/UVA2 v\u00e0 UVB.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1ea5t b\u1ec1n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng (photostable) v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng cho nh\u1eefng m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n (v\u00ed d\u1ee5 <\/span><b>avobenzone<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">), nh\u1edd v\u1eady gi\u1eef v\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t sau ph\u01a1i n\u1eafng.<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/promo.basf.com\/campaign\/Projetos\/CaringForYou\/Documentos\/Geral\/Tinosorb%C2%AE%20S.pdf?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng (\u201cperformance booster\u201d): khi gh\u00e9p c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c UVB m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Ethylhexyl Triazone\/Uvinul T150 ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng Uvinul A Plus (UVA m\u1ea1nh), h\u1ec7 l\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t cao v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc <\/span><b>h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng UV v\u00e0 <\/span><b>gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng nhi\u1ec7t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i k\u00edch th\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA, oxy ho\u00e1 lipid v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 do tia UV. (Infographic minh ho\u1ea1 chu tr\u00ecnh h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 \u2192 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.)<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-hop-toi-uu\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1<\/b><b>i \u01b0u?<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i \u201ckinh \u0111i\u1ec3n\u201d:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Tinosorb S + Uvinul A Plus (Diethylamino Hydroxybenzoyl Hexyl Benzoate):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gia c\u01b0\u1eddng UVA1\/UVA2, t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Tinosorb S + Uvinul T150 (Ethylhexyl Triazone):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u201cch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n\u201d UVB c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh \u2192 SPF cao v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ecdn.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Tinosorb S + Avobenzone:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Tinosorb S \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 <\/span><b>\u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">cho avobenzone (k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c).<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i EU cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00f3m triazine (BEMT, Ethylhexyl Triazone) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho tr\u1ebb em \u2013 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 l\u1ecdc n\u00e0y khi tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-kem-chong-nang-co-tinosorb-s\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 Tinosorb S<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-kcn-co-tinosorb-s-dung-tot-nhat-khi-nao\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng KCN c\u00f3 Tinosorb S d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 UVA-PF\/PPD cao (Tinosorb S + Uvinul A Plus), b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o ho\u1eb7c \u1ea9m nh\u1eb9 tu\u1ef3 n\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi\/l\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1eafng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Ch\u1ecdn water-resistant, c\u00f3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Uvinul T150\/Octyl Triazone \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n UVB, v\u00e0 Tinosorb S \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng UVA-PF sau nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd.<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.littlewonderland.nl\/en\/blogs\/beauty-blog\/sun-protection-the-ultimate-guide\/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>Da d\u1ea7u\/da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u01afu ti\u00ean gel-cream\/light lotion\/milk ch\u1ee9a Tinosorb S v\u00ec t\u00ednh tan trong d\u1ea7u gi\u00fap da kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng b\u00ed.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Quan s\u00e1t n\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c (h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u\/c\u1ed3n\/solvent) nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc; ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u201csensitive\u201d c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng uy t\u00edn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-chong-chi-dinhkhong-nen-ket-hop-voi-chat-nao-khong\"><\/span><b>C\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh\/kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Avobenzone \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n; n\u00ean \u0111i k\u00e8m ch\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng (trong \u0111\u00f3 <\/span><b>Tinosorb S<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201c\u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng\u201d \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh gi\u1eefa Tinosorb S v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c; \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ma tr\u1eadn c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c (solvent, polymer, ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1) b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8168 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-3.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc tinosorb S kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phu-nu-co-thaicho-con-bu-co-dung-duoc-tinosorb-s-khong\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai\/cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tinosorb S kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u1eadt l\u00fd Zinc Oxide\/Titanium Dioxide th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem an to\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t cho ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1 nh\u01b0 Tinosorb S, \u1edf c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t (EU\u2026), s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t; tuy v\u1eady, nh\u00f3m thai k\u1ef3\/cho con b\u00fa v\u1eabn n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8169\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8169\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8169 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-4.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t g\u1eaft gao h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng US\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/89-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8169\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t g\u1eaft gao h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng US<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>V\u00ec sao nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u00edch d\u00f9ng Tinosorb S nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p \u1edf Hoa K\u1ef3?<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 \u00dac l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u0103ng. M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Tinosorb S kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho tr\u1ebb em. Tinosorb S c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng,gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 khu\u1ebfch \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 SPF\/UVA-PF khi ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00fang, nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t cao h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f2n \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Hoa K\u1ef3 do quy tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecbnh cho ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, n\u00ean Tinosorb S CH\u01afA \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5. Quy tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 3\/2026.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tin, A. (2024, October 2). FDA now weighing approval of first new sunscreen ingredient in decades. Cbsnews.com; CBS News. https:\/\/www.cbsnews.com\/news\/fda-new-sunscreen-ingredient-review-bemotrizinol\/<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200c<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tinosorb S (Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol Methoxyphenyl Triazine\/BEMT) \u2013 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8170,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8165","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8165","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8165"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8165\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8172,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8165\/revisions\/8172"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.v